{
  "page_title": "批量更新发票状态",
  "apis": [
    {
      "group_title": "批量更新发票状态",
      "api_name": "updatestatusbatch",
      "method": "POST",
      "api_url": "https://qyapi.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/card/invoice/reimburse/updatestatusbatch",
      "description": "发票平台可以通过该接口对某个成员的一批发票进行锁定、解锁和报销操作。注意，报销状态为不可逆状态，请开发者慎重调用。",
      "query_params": [
        {
          "name": "access_token",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "调用接口凭证"
        }
      ],
      "body_params": [
        {
          "name": "openid",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "用户openid，可用[\"userid与openid互换接口\"](#11279)获取"
        },
        {
          "name": "reimburse_status",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "发票报销状态 INVOICE_REIMBURSE_INIT：发票初始状态，未锁定；INVOICE_REIMBURSE_LOCK：发票已锁定，无法重复提交报销;INVOICE_REIMBURSE_CLOSURE:发票已核销，从用户卡包中移除"
        },
        {
          "name": "invoice_list",
          "type": "object[]",
          "required": true,
          "description": "发票列表，必须全部属于同一个openid"
        },
        {
          "name": "invoice_list[].card_id",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "发票卡券的card_id"
        },
        {
          "name": "invoice_list[].encrypt_code",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "发票卡券的加密code，和card_id共同构成一张发票卡券的唯一标识"
        }
      ],
      "response_params": [
        {
          "name": "errcode",
          "type": "int32",
          "required": false,
          "description": "错误码"
        },
        {
          "name": "errmsg",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "错误信息"
        }
      ],
      "request_examples": [
        {
          "title": "示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n   \"openid\":\"OPENID\" ,\n   \"reimburse_status\":\"INVOICE_REIMBURSE_INIT\",\n    \"invoice_list\":\n    [\n        {\"card_id\":\"cardid_1\",\"encrypt_code\":\"encrypt_code_1\"},\n        {\"card_id\":\"cardid_2\",\"encrypt_code\":\"encrypt_code_2\"}\n    ]\n}"
        }
      ],
      "response_examples": [
        {
          "title": "示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n   \"errcode\":0,\n   \"errmsg\":\"ok\",\n}"
        }
      ],
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "权限说明",
          "content": "仅认证的企业微信账号有接口权限"
        },
        {
          "title": "注",
          "content": "1. 报销方须保证在报销、锁定、解锁后及时将状态同步至微信端，保证用户发票可以正常使用\n2. 批量更新发票状态接口为事务性操作，如果其中一张发票更新失败，列表中的其它发票状态更新也会无法执行，恢复到接口调用前的状态"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}